snippet.title: Brawlout Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/brawlout-switch 

Brawlout is the party fighting game, designed for couch play, online 
matches and competitive tournaments.

A NEW CHALLENGER HAS APPEARED IN THE PLATFORM FIGHTER ARENA!

For more details, follow @brawloutgame : https://twitter.com/brawloutgame
